ommentaries Open Letter Of Georgian Theologians To The Holy Synod Of Orthodox Church Of Georgia Support The Holy And Great Council].''\n* ''[http://myocn.net/26054-2/ Holy Cross Greek Orthodox School Of Theology Statement On The Great And Holy Council].''\n* ''[http://panorthodoxcemes.blogspot.com/ International, Multilingual Blog On The Great And Holy Council].'' \n* ''[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NCBybW7Z2X0 Message from His All-Holiness on the Holy and Great Council - Ecumenical Patriarchate Press Office].'' His All-Holiness Ecumenical Patriarch Bartholomew (YouTube). May 13, 2016.\n* Archdeacon and Ecumenical Patriarchate spokesman John Chryssavgis. ''[http://www.firstthings.com/web-exclusives/2016/02/on-the-great-council-of-the-orthodox-church On the Great Council of the Orthodox Church].'' First Things. Feb. 3, 2016.\n\n'''Criticism'''\n* ''' ''[http://www.pravoslavie.ru/english/94095.htm The Holy And Great Council: Discussion].'' Orthodox Christianity (Pravoslavie.ru)'''. (''pathfinder to numerous articles mostly against the Council '')\n* ''[https://mospat.ru/en/2016/02/02/news127677/ Patriarch Kirill: We Do Not Call The Forthcoming Pan-Orthodox Council Ecumenical].'' \n* ''[https://mospat.ru/en/2016/06/03/news132577/ Session Of The Holy Synod Of The Russian Orthodox Church 3 June 2016, Proceedings No. 35].'' \n* ''[http://www.pravoslavie.ru/english/94019.htm Orthodox Church Of Cyprus Has Proposed Amendments To The Text \"Relations Of The Orthodox Church With The Rest Of The Christian World\"].'' \n* ''[http://www.antiochpatriarchate.org/en/page/1436/ Statement of the Secretariat of the Antiochian Holy Synod].'' \n* ''[http://www.pravoslavie.ru/english/93965.htm Conclusions Of The Theological-Academic Conference: The Holy And Great Council: With Great Preparation But Without Expectations].'' Transl. Fr. Nicholas K. Orthodox Christianity (Pravoslavie.ru). June 4, 2016.\n* ''[http://www.antiochpatriarchate.org/en/page/1434/ A Statement Issued by the Secret